Matthew Lawrence https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matthew_Lawrence 0 Matthew William Lawrence (born February 11, 1980) is an American actor and singer known for his roles as Chris Hillard in Mrs. Doubtfire, Jack Hunter in Boy Meets World, Billy in The Hot Chick, Sam Collins in Superhuman Samurai Syber-Squad, and Matt Roman in Brotherly Love.
